<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.7">
<l>eṉṟu moṉṟāki yottārummikkārkaḷun taṉṟaṉak</l>
<l>kiṉṟi niṉṟāṉai yellāvulaku muṭaiyāṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kuṉṟa moṉṟāṉ maḻaikāttapirāṉaiccoṉ mālaikaḷ</l>
<l>naṉṟu cūṭṭum vitiyeytiṉa meṉṉa kuṟainamakkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who, being always one thing, stands without anybody who is equal</l>
<l>or more than him, he who possesses all the worlds,</l>
<l>the lord who protected against the rain with a single mountain, we have reached</l>
<l>a mode [of life] of well putting word garlands on him. What want [would there be] for us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
